message: Focus on creating a 3-animal hybrid that includes land, water, and air features. Use Growth Serum (ğŸŒ¡ï¸) once or twice on small/medium animals to get them to value 10-15; avoid super-growing large animals (applying growth twice), as it often turns their value negative.
